fields.name: Estimated income
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount est: income'))

fields.name: Actual income
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: income'))

fields.name: Living expenses
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: living expenses'))

fields.name: Food expenses
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: food expenses'))

fields.name: Transportation expenses
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: transportation expenses'))

fields.name: Personal expenses
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: personal expenses'))

fields.name: Entertainment expenses
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: entertainment expenses'))

fields.name: Loan payments
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: loans'))

fields.name: Contributions
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: contributions'))

fields.name: Other expenses
fields.formula: sum(field('Amount: other expenses'))

fields.name: Total estimated expenses
fields.formula:
sum(field("Amount est: living expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount est: food expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount est: transportation expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount est: personal expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount est: entertainment expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount est: loans")) 
+ sum(field("Amount est: contributions")) 
+ sum(field("Amount est: other expenses"))

fields.name: Total actual expenses
fields.formula:
sum(field("Amount: living expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount: food expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount: transportation expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount: personal expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount: entertainment expenses")) 
+ sum(field("Amount: loans")) 
+ sum(field("Amount: contributions")) 
+ sum(field("Amount: other expenses"))

fields.name: Estimated balance
fields.formula:
if(sum(field("Amount est: income")) < 0, 
    0, 
    sum(field("Amount est: income")) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: living expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: food expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: transportation expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: personal expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: entertainment expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: loans")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: contributions")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount est: other expenses")), 0) 
)

fields.name: Actual balance
fields.formula:
if(sum(field("Amount: income")) < 0, 
    0, 
    sum(field("Amount: income")) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: living expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: food expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: transportation expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: personal expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: entertainment expenses")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: loans")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: contributions")), 0) 
        - when_empty(sum(field("Amount: other expenses")), 0) 
)

fields.name: Odd or even
fields.formula:
if(
    equal(
        search(
            totext(
                divide(month(todate(field("Period")+"-01", "YYYY-MM-DD")), 
                2)), 
            ".5"), 
        0
    ), 
    true, false
)
